results.description:
Me and doggo went to hike through a Swedish forest. We couldn’t find the hiking trail so we just went into the unexplored parts (that turned to be just 200 meters below the actual path). 
Unexpectedly we saw a deer jump out from behind a massive rock.  She ran away onto higher grounds and was probably observing us from there. 
The doggo sniffed something next to a tree, and for a few seconds i tried to understand what it was. The natural camouflage was working spectacularly well, the animal’s fur and the environment around were almost seamless. 
That was a baby deer.
